text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed's Graphing Calculator replicates the TI-84 Plus CE workflow on a modern, high-resolution canvas. Plot functions, solve matrices, run statistics, and compute probability distributions with full keyboard navigation. Supports degree and radian modes, parametric and polar graphing, and table mode. No sign-up — a free alternative to TI-84 Online, Desmos Premium, and GeoGebra Pro.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"HD Function Graphing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Plot up to 10 functions simultaneously — standard, parametric, and polar. Pan, zoom, and trace with a modern canvas renderer that makes TI-84's 96×64 pixel screen look ancient.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Statistics & Regression\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Enter data into lists L1–L6, compute 1-Var Stats, and run LinReg, QuadReg, ExpReg, and PwrReg — with correlation coefficients and scatter plots.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Matrix Operations\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Work with up to 10 matrices [A]–[J]. Add, multiply, find determinants, compute inverses, and row-reduce to RREF — all with a proper grid editor.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Distribution Functions\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"normalcdf, invNorm, tcdf, binompdf, chi-square, and Poisson — the same distribution functions from the TI-84 DISTR menu, with shaded area visualizations.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{}]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Free Online Graphing Calculator — TI-84 Alternative\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed's graphing calculator brings TI-84 functionality to your browser with a modern, high-definition interface. Plot functions in crisp detail instead of on a 96×64 pixel screen. Run linear regressions, compute matrix operations, and evaluate distribution functions — all without buying a $100+ calculator or downloading a sketchy ROM emulator. Every calculation is verified against TI-84 reference outputs with over 200 automated tests, so you can trust the results for homework, exams, and research.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Plot up to 10 functions simultaneously with individual colors\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],\"Plot up to 10 functions simultaneously with individual colors\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Standa