alculator replicates the TI-84 Plus CE workflow on a modern, high-resolution canvas. Plot functions, solve matrices, run statistics, and compute probability distributions with full keyboard navigation. Supports degree and radian modes, parametric and polar graphing, and table mode. No sign-up — a free alternative to TI-84 Online, Desmos Premium, and GeoGebra Pro.\"}]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"HD Function Graphing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Plot up to 10 functions simultaneously — standard, parametric, and polar. Pan, zoom, and trace with a modern canvas renderer that makes TI-84's 96×64 pixel screen look ancient.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Statistics & Regression\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Enter data into lists L1–L6, compute 1-Var Stats, and run LinReg, QuadReg, ExpReg, and PwrReg — with correlation coefficients and scatter plots.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Matrix Operations\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Work with up to 10 matrices [A]–[J]. Add, multiply, find determinants, compute inverses, and row-reduce to RREF — all with a proper grid editor.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Distribution Functions\"}],[\